### ── (optional) See everything you just generated, newest first ─────────────
GET {{srv}}/odata/v4/log/GeneratedDocuments?$select=ID,fileName,documentNumber,status,size,generatedAt&$orderby=generatedAt desc&$top=20
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access_token}}


### ── (optional) Download one PDF — put a documentId from a response above ────
GET {{srv}}/api/v1/documents/PASTE_documentId/download
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access_token}}